{"tid":1263550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《撐》台灣香港音樂一起《撐》港人！","createTime":"2019-06-28T08:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:34:02.000Z","uid":115096,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34368c8d8f2fc7ba58391b0778617dc48438ee80","tid":1263550,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssCWcBNqvnc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DssCWcBNqvnc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=85746608\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssCWcBNqvnc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"8d77f6364b8c8faf63e64e0e30d08c3759f22d69","tid":1263550,"uid":447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"謝謝台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人要爭氣！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 我地而家基本訴求一個都達唔到<br />\n冇撤回<br />\n冇成立黑警調查組<br />\n冇還到義士清白<br />\n冇撤銷暴動<br />\n<br />\n有人擋喺你前面捱打同死諫<br />\n有人坐完政治監出返嚟都要再努力<br />\n有人喺獄中幾希望可以真正地參與其中<br />\n<br />\n你有咩原因唔出嚟！<br />\n你有咩原因鬆懈！<br />\n你有咩原因唔為自己好好真正地爭取！<br />\n<br />\n時代革命，光復香港！<br />\n<br />\n大家記得今晚帶餐具去野餐！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b91aa94eb3feefa084ff5c11838ed85a53a73468","tid":1263550,"uid":195650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"果時撐起雨傘班群星<br />\n完全不見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc0cc4d5dfc688f655172a65e4484d153ef58fe","tid":1263550,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b6eb0a21d6075fe26d9065f97faacf6c0f6138","tid":1263550,"uid":249526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad8f1f15ac1e9ec8e40deb9fa659d51d796e4a12","tid":1263550,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018f6e2d133ef1e89035cf0b2ed722ab2a9d6782","tid":1263550,"uid":176114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b91aa94eb3feefa084ff5c11838ed85a53a73468","tid":1263550,"uid":195650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"果時撐起雨傘班群星<br />\n完全不見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"今次係台灣做主導 只係邀請hocc明哥<br />\n同雨革唔同"},{"pid":"534ec169683a6c86dc45d61e5f282acb8756e49b","tid":1263550,"uid":176114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"多謝台灣 多謝夕爺 多謝hocc &amp; 明哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c739f8976f1bb2835d66885ba535daee056722b","tid":1263550,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"《撐》 <br />\n詞：武雄、林夕 <br />\n曲：吳永吉 <br />\n編曲：董事長樂團 <br />\n製作人：柯智豪<br />\n<br />\n風吹不停 雨還在下 <br />\n你留下的訊息 我看見啦 <br />\n路很遙遠 腳不能停下 <br />\n天黑了的夜晚 就點燃燭光 <br />\n雨越下越急越狂 淋濕了去向 <br />\n讓我們撐起傘 不放棄 不退讓 <br />\n不怕黑夜有多長 永遠無法阻擋 <br />\n攜手翻越傲慢的高牆 <br />\n不怕黑夜多冰涼 要更勇敢 <br />\n撐起希望一直到天亮 <br />\n路還很漫長 心要更堅強 <br />\n天黑了的夜晚 我在你身旁 <br />\n雨越下越急越狂 淋不濕夢想 <br />\n讓我們撐起傘 不放棄 不退讓 <br />\n（粵） <br />\n走上不獻媚的路 腳步注定緩慢 <br />\n不信得我一個人企硬 <br />\n普世真理無界限 不必孤單 <br />\n越弱越燦爛 越難越撐 <br />\n不管黑夜有多長（粵）拋棄小我無界限  <br />\n永遠無法阻擋（粵）價值拒絕糜爛 <br />\n攜手翻越傲慢的高牆（粵）企硬 <br />\n（粵） <br />\n不信竟有牆不爛 <br />\n多麼小的雞蛋 <br />\n平凡而偉大 越難越撐 <br />\n憑頑強信念 越難越撐"}]}